<head>

<title>If my Lord asks me</title>

</head>

<body bgcolor= "dadbf0">


<h1 align="center">

If my Lord asks me "have you (any) shame in disobeying Me?". <br/>

You conceal your sins  from my creation, and with sins you come to me".<br/>

So how will I answer? O woe to me, and who shall protect me?<br/>

I keep averting my soul with thoughts of hope from time to time.<br/>

And I forget what is to come after death, what is to come after am shrouded. <br/>

As if am guaranteed life (eternally) and that death will not come to me. <br/>

And when the severity of death overtakes me, who will protect me.<br/>

I looked at the faces, is there not from amongst them who will ransom me? <br/>

I will be asked regarding what I have prepared in my life to save me (on the day of judgement). <br/>

Then how will I answer after I have neglected my religion. <br/>

Woe to me! Did I not hear the speech of Allah inviting me?<br/>

Did I not hear what came in (the chapters) of QAF and YAASIN? <br/>

Did I not hear about the of gathering, the day of Judgement. <br/>

Did I  not hear the caller of death inviting me, calling me?<br/>

So O my Lord, a slave (<i>turning to you</I>), I have repented so who then shall shelter me?<br/>

Excpet a Lord extensive in forgiveness - To the truth He will Guide me.<br/>

I have come to You (in repetance), so have mercy on me,and make my scales heavy (with good deeds).<br/>

And lighten my account - You are the best of those who will bring me to account.<br/>

</h1>

<br>
<br>
<br>

<h1 align="center">

<p><font color="grey">Ikiwa bwana wangu ananiuliza "una (a) yoyote aibu kwa kuniasi?". <br/>

Unaficha dhambi zako kwa uumbaji wangu, na kwa dhambi unakuja kwangu ".<br/>

Kwa hivyo nitajibuje? Ole wangu, ni nani atanilinda?<br/>

Ninaendelea kuizuia roho yangu na mawazo ya tumaini mara kwa mara.<br/>

Na mimi husahau kitakachokuja baada ya kifo, kitakachokuja baada ya kuvikwa. <br/>

Kama kwamba nimehakikishiwa maisha ya milele na kwamba mauti hayatakuja kwangu. <br/>

Na ukali wa kifo utakaponipata, nani atanilinda.<br/>

Niliangalia nyuso, je! Hakuna kati yao atakayenikomboa? <br/>

Nitaulizwa kuhusu kile nimeandaa katika maisha yangu kuniokoa (siku ya hukumu). <br/>

Halafu nitajibuje baada ya kupuuza dini yangu. <br/>

Ole wangu! Sijasikia hotuba ya Mwenyezi Mungu ikinialika?<br/>

Sikusikia kile kilichoingia (sura) za QAF na YAASIN? <br/>

Je! Sikusikia habari ya siku ya kukusanyika, Siku ya Hukumu. <br/>

Sikusikia mpigaji wa kifo akinialika, akiniita?<br/>

Kwa hivyo Mola wangu Mlezi, mtumwa (nimekugeukia), nimeitubu kwa hivyo nani atanihifadhi?<br/>

Utafta Mola katika msamaha- Kwa ukweli ataniongoza.<br/>

Nimekujia (kwa kurudisha), kwa hivyo unirehemu, na uzanie mizani yangu iwe nzito (na vitendo vizuri).<br/>

Na nipunguze akaunti yangu - Wewe ndiye bora zaidi ya wale ambao watanileta hesabu.<br/></font></p>

</h1>



